Here are some rpm related scripts distributed under GPLv3+.

* COPYING.GPLv3: license file
* README: this file
* list-requires-by-package-name.sh: list required rpms by package name
* list-srpmnames-by-file.sh: list names of src.rpms by file
* rpm2json.py: dump json expression of rpm metadata
* rpms2sqldb.py: scan rpm files and generated metadata database (sqlite)
* pmaker.py: "super" packaging tool. gen package (tgz, rpm, deb) from files
  list, etc. Successor of xpack.py and filelist2rpm.py.
* xpack.py: "super" packaging tool. gen package (tgz, rpm, deb) from file list


NOTES
========================

* filelist2rpm.py and xpack.py were removed as these are replaced with its
  successor, pmaker.py



Author
